	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Monetalis. In MRR 2.441, substitute Gar(gonius) for Gar(gilius), and both there and in the Index, 570, refer also to Crawford, RRC 1.364-366, no. 350A, 86 B.C. On Gargonius, see Cicero, Brut. 180; Syme, Historia 13, 1964, 117-RP 2.595; Wiseman, NM 233, no. 193, with a query.\n" .
